snippet.title: ShowBiz Minute: Heard, Legend, Box Office
snippet.description:
Amber Heard avoids jail in Australian dog smuggling spat; John Legend, Chrissy Teigen welcome baby girl, Luna Simone; 'Jungle Book' roars with $103.6 million debut at the U.S. box office. (April 18)
